screen_desc: The screenshot displays a mobile app interface for setting a destination. The top section shows the current time and connectivity icons. Below, the destination options include "Đại Lý MobizPay 47" and "mega mall." There are buttons to add home and work locations. Further down, it lists "Vincom Mega Mall Thảo Điền" with its address in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. A keyboard is visible at the bottom, indicating the user can input text.
